Subject: RE: [T2] Engine to Tranny - 3 bolts?

I have an VW powered trike that I built. When I got the engine and
transmission for it, the engine was only being held on by 2 bolts. One on
each side, opposite corners. The started only had one of the bolts. It was
being driven around in a bug for who knows how long like this. Still works
good today with all bolts and not parts replaced.

Corbett

